{"tid":1815314,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃藍藥房 又係分黃藍嘅時候","createTime":"2020-01-07T12:09:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-08T10:39:56.000Z","uid":264071,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"5c6258ad681bac716ee8ec3d83e142397aa63345","tid":1815314,"uid":264071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T12:09:13.000Z","msg":"【旺角有藥房大幅加價 50個口罩賣498元】<br />\n<br />\n武漢爆發不明肺炎，從武漢回港須通報的個案增至三十宗，口罩又成為搶手貨。在旺角，有藥房將口罩放在當眼地方售賣，一盒50個的外科口罩賣498元，平均一個口罩價值近十元。不願意透露身分的負責人指，早前仍賣50元一盒外科口罩，即使加至近500元一盒，一天內仍賣出約一百盒。<br />\n<br />\n藥房負責人指，加價是因為來貨價上升，但沒透露升幅。<br />\n<br />\n#香港電台 #藥房 #口罩<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/715486135226112/posts/3120081534766548/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F715486135226112%2Fposts%2F3120081534766548%2F&d=rLp99s1CaA%2FTm5LA4NL6Tf1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=3e70221e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/715486135226112/posts/3120081534766548/</a>"},{"pid":"352efa155e7ed9a007cb62c5689be4c84a9c82f9","tid":1815314,"uid":264071,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T12:12:09.000Z","msg":"加價還加價，加都加得有良心啲，加到天價就準備收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黃藥房可以上黎講，等大家幫襯下，簿利多消<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abfbc8af59dd4084642c7b129582992cc85a7d32","tid":1815314,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T12:12:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n環保罩<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"366ff80cd840e93f083fd50bd746f8cbe9df534b","tid":1815314,"uid":23169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T12:17:27.000Z","msg":"我都想知自己區有咩黃藥房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d99650c52ebbcc923eab8a89a80800c25c0d0f38","tid":1815314,"uid":112581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3